{"tid":375155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（和理非非地抗爭）頭先捐左堆外國coins畀政府。","createTime":"2017-08-26T10:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T05:23:44.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86a664b6463e42a40e0dccf2cc9533418d95cba6","tid":375155,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無留意，公立醫院大堂，會放置捐款箱既呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（捐款箱位置link：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/ha_visitor_text_index.asp?Content_ID=225125&amp;lang=CHIB5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fvisitor%2Fha_visitor_text_index.asp%3FContent_ID%3D225125%26lang%3DCHIB5&d=u%2FisQfE7dO%2Ff33Jj%2BdeHbuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0caf547d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ha.org.hk/visitor/ha_visitor_text_index.asp?Content_ID=225125&amp;lang=CHIB5</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說，醫管局財務部有個夾萬，係用黎專係放呢d善款既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要擺夾萬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為有部份善款並唔係香港流通貨幣，有又入唔到落銀行。即係外國碎銀、舊版外國鈔票、好舊款既港紙之類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫管局財務部既員工呢，聽講，係要定期點算呢d「得物無所用」既善款，去確保數目準確，無少到既。<br />\n<br />\n你無睇錯，係要定期拎出黎逐個銀仔，逐款貨幣數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左進一步加重薪高糧準、平時準時放工既公務員既負擔，我決定將平時用淨既外國銀仔，放晒入呢d捐款箱度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以威記為例，下面呢款係「威記慈善基金捐款箱」，大家咪認錯，我地目標唔系呢個！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/181554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F181554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9f9909b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿，下圖左面果個，先係「醫管局專用捐款箱」，認住佢！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/181733_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F181733_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=943c0b04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d40a30657426b60cacbab3198234bed6138ac12","tid":375155,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b257697e6d5da626d2176d8d5d9d76e9fa5a46b","tid":375155,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫院管理局僱員唔係公務員</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有部份合約工，有部份有長俸既員工"},{"pid":"56944113584dae7b4bf1b7216c36a776a24f19b7","tid":375155,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f9b340e94416bb23dcaded36c21416e0065ad9","tid":375155,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91fd9e189c59c0e9b451c6c3b31a8e78e48669cf","tid":375155,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"754db499e58c49316aa09ed8cad9191764985b1c","tid":375155,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9</blockquote><br />\n點解呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非非喎。左膠最愛"},{"pid":"bb0781bce79c7e106011a02c9965a036f5e4c4b5","tid":375155,"uid":48838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"on9無藥醫"}]}